    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the plan I've written:\n\n## PulseBoard Channel Plugin — Implementation Plan\n\n**15 new files** under `extensions/pulseboard/` only. Zero existing file modifications.\n\n### File overview\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `openclaw.plugin.json` | Minimal manifest (`id: \"pulseboard\"`, `channels: [\"pulseboard\"]`) |\n| `package.json` | npm metadata + `openclaw.channel` block (id, label, blurb, aliases, npmSpec) |\n| `index.ts` | `defineChannelPluginEntry` wiring plugin + runtime setter |\n| `setup-entry.ts` | `defineSetupPluginEntry` lightweight setup loader |\n| `api.ts` | Public barrel → re-exports `runtime-api` |\n| `runtime-api.ts` | SDK re-export barrel (sourced from public `openclaw/plugin-sdk/*` subpaths since no `openclaw/plugin-sdk/pulseboard` facade exists yet) |\n| `src/types.ts` | `PulseBoardAccountConfig`, `ResolvedPulseBoardAccount`, `resolvePulseBoardAccount()` |\n| `src/config-schema.ts` | Zod schema for `channels.pulseboard.*` (apiToken, serverUrl, dmPolicy, allowFrom) |\n| `src/runtime.ts` | `createPluginRuntimeStore` → `get/setPulseBoardRuntime` |\n| `src/client.ts` | Fictional `PulseBoardClient` stub (sendDirectMessage, postToBoard, verifyToken) |\n| `src/normalize.ts` | `@username` → `username`, `#board` → `#board`; `isBoardTarget`, `looksLikePulseBoardTargetId` |\n| `src/send.ts` | Routes outbound to DM or board via client; wraps result with `attachChannelToResult` |\n| `src/setup-core.ts` | `ChannelSetupAdapter.applyAccountConfig` |\n| `src/setup-surface.ts` | Two-step wizard (apiToken + optional serverUrl) |\n| `src/channel.ts` | `createChatChannelPlugin` with `chatTypes: [\"direct\", \"group\"]`, `textChunkLimit: 4000`, DM pairing, security, outbound, gateway |\n\n### Key design decisions\n- **Naming invariants** (`bundled-plugin-naming.test.ts`): all four alignment rules satisfied (`@openclaw/pulseboard`, dir `pulseboard/`, manifest id `pulseboard`, `channel.id pulseboard`, `npmSpec == name`)\n- **Modeled on Nostr** for single-account/top-level config + DM pairing, plus **IRC** for group (`#board`) routing\n- **No external deps** — fictional client is a pure stub\n- **`runtime-api.ts`** imports from public `openclaw/plugin-sdk/*` subpaths directly (since `openclaw/plugin-sdk/pulseboard` doesn't exist and can't be added without modifying core)",
